Comment.value:
Initial Selected, before ritual

This is Fenthick in the room within castle never that the player is transported to when they bring the fourth creature to Aribeth in the temple of tyr
Fenthick has 2 selecteds for before the ritual

The room has 4 priests of Tyr doing conjuration in the middle of the room around an altar.
The player has to speak with Aribeth, Desther, Fenthick, and Lord Never before the ritual continues. Locals are set when the player LEAVES dialogue with them.
Once the player has spoken to all four, Aribeth, Desther and Fenthick move into position with the four priests.
Spell effects begin firing.
After a big flourish, Fenthick will say that it is complete.
Desther will then cast a spell and say that now is the time to strike.
Desther says one more line and then disappears. The portal he creates does not end when he disappears
Fenthick yells out to him and runs into the portal.
Aribeth begins casting, ignoring everyone around her. She is "keeping the portal open"
Now everyone is in post ritual mode, but will not say more than a single line until all the invading Helmites are defeated.
Player goes through the portal, appears outside Helm's Hold.
player has spoken to Aribeth, Nasher, Desther.
